---
import ChapterLayout from '../layouts/ChapterLayout.astro';
---

<ChapterLayout title="Home">
  <div class="hero">
    <h1>Epic EHI Manual - Astro POC</h1>
    <p>This is a proof of concept for migrating the Epic EHI Manual to Astro.</p>
    
    <h2>Features Demonstrated:</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Static HTML generation with Astro</li>
      <li>Client-side SQL execution with SQL.js</li>
      <li>Progressive enhancement (works without JavaScript)</li>
      <li>React components for interactivity</li>
      <li>Clean, modern design</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Sample Chapter:</h2>
    <p><a href="/ehi-manual/chapters/02.2-the-identifier-trinity.html">Chapter 2.2: The Identifier Trinity</a></p>

    <h2>Architecture:</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Build-time query extraction from markdown</li>
      <li>Static file output for GitHub Pages</li>
      <li>No server-side code required</li>
      <li>SQL runs entirely in the browser via WebAssembly</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</ChapterLayout>

